sequenceDiagram
    participant CLI as Server CLI
    participant Builder as ClaudeClientBuilder
    participant Cmd as subprocess::Command
    participant Claude as Claude Process
    participant Collector as OTEL Collector
    participant Dashboard as GM Dashboard

    CLI->>Builder: --otel-endpoint http://localhost:4318
    Note over Builder: otel_endpoint: Some(url)

    Builder->>Cmd: .env("OTEL_EXPORTER_OTLP_ENDPOINT", url)
    Builder->>Cmd: .env("OTEL_SERVICE_NAME", "sidequest-claude")
    Builder->>Cmd: .env("OTEL_TRACES_EXPORTER", "otlp")
    Builder->>Cmd: .env("OTEL_METRICS_EXPORTER", "otlp")
    Builder->>Cmd: .env("OTEL_LOGS_EXPORTER", "otlp")
    Builder->>Cmd: .env("CLAUDE_CODE_ENABLE_TELEMETRY", "1")
    Builder->>Cmd: .env("CLAUDE_CODE_OTEL_FLUSH_TIMEOUT_MS", "3000")

    Cmd->>Claude: spawn() with inherited env
    Claude-->>Collector: OTLP spans (tool calls, tokens, duration)
    Collector-->>Dashboard: broadcast via 21-2 OTLP receiver

    Note over Builder: otel_endpoint: None
    Builder->>Cmd: spawn() — no env vars set
    Note over Cmd: Clean subprocess, zero OTEL overhead